{
  "title": "Light Creamy Canadian Tofu Bake",
  "description": "A sour, creamy, and light Canadian-inspired dish featuring silken tofu, perfect for a weeknight dinner or a casual get-together. This recipe is easy to make and packed with nutritious ingredients.",
  "cuisine": "canadian",
  "diet": [
    "vegetarian",
